<section id="tarifs" class="py-24 px-6 bg-main-bg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-20">
    <span class="reveal text-[#6352ff] text-base mb-4 block font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">// Tarifs</span>
    <h2 class="reveal text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black uppercase text-title leading-tight mb-4">
      Des offres taillées<br><span class="text-gradient-pink italic">pour l'excellence.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal text-title/70 text-sm max-w-2xl leading-relaxed italic">
      Chaque projet est unique. Ces formules constituent une base de prix.<br> Je suis à votre écoute pour un devis sur-mesure.
    </p>
  </div>


  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto items-stretch">
    
    <div class="reveal delay-100 group relative mx-auto w-full max-w-90 md:max-w-none bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-[32px] p-8 border border-title/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 border-b border-title/5 pb-6">
          <div>
            <span class="uppercase text-[9px] font-black tracking-widest text-title/40 bg-title/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Essentiel</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase text-title mt-3 leading-tight">Site<br/>Mono-page</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black text-title italic line-through">800</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-0.5">€</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline">
              <span class="text-5xl font-black text-title italic">400</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-0.5">€</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-title/20 tracking-tighter">À partir de</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-title/60 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-8">Parfait pour une présence en ligne rapide et un message percutant. Tout sur une seule page fluide.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/70">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3"></div> Design Unique & Responsive (Tablette & Mobile)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/70">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3"></div> Optimisation SEO
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/70">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3"></div> Site sécurisé
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/70">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3"></div> Animation Prenium
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/70">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3"></div> Section Contact Directe
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <a href="#contact" class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl border border-title/10 text-title text-center text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-title hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">Démarrer</a>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal delay-200 group relative mx-auto w-full max-w-90 md:max-w-none bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 border border-[#6352ff]/10 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-4 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col justify-between border-t-4 border-t-[#6352ff]">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-8 -translate-y-1/2 bg-[#6352ff] text-white text-[9px] font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">Populaire</div>
      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 border-b border-title/5 pb-6">
          <div>
            <span class="uppercase text-[9px] font-black tracking-widest text-[#6352ff] bg-[#6352ff]/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Standard</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase text-title mt-3 leading-tight">Site<br/>Vitrine</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold line-through">1200</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold">€</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline">
              <span class="text-5xl font-black text-title italic">600</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-0.5">€</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-title/20 tracking-tighter">À partir de</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-title/60 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-8">L'offre idéale pour présenter votre expertise sur 1 à 5 pages optimisées.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3 shadow-glow"></div> Design & Responsive (Tablette & Mobile)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3 shadow-glow"></div> Structure Multi-pages
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3 shadow-glow"></div> Optimisation SEO
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3 shadow-glow"></div> Site Sécurisé
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3 shadow-glow"></div> Animations Premium
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-title/80">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#6352ff] mr-3 shadow-glow"></div> Page de Contact
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <a href="#contact" class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl bg-title text-white text-center text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#6352ff] transition-all duration-300">Choisir cette offre</a>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal delay-300 group relative mx-auto w-full max-w-90 md:max-w-none bg-title rounded-[32px] p-8 border border-white/5 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
          <div>
            <span class="uppercase text-[9px] font-black tracking-widest text-white/40 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">E-Commerce</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase text-white mt-3 leading-tight">Boutique<br/>En ligne</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black text-white italic line-through">3500</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-0.5">€</span>
            </div>
              <span class="text-5xl font-black text-white italic">1750</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[#6352ff] ml-0.5">€</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-white/20 tracking-tighter">À partir de</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-8">Une machine à vendre robuste avec gestion de stock et paiements sécurisés.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-white/90">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#d363ff] mr-3"></div> Design & Responsive (Tablette & Mobile)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-white/90">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#d363ff] mr-3"></div> CMS (Gestion Produits)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-white/90">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#d363ff] mr-3"></div> Stripe / PayPal Intégrés
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-white/90">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#d363ff] mr-3"></div> Site Sécurisé
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-white/90">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#d363ff] mr-3"></div> Animation Prenium
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-[13px] font-bold text-white/90">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#d363ff] mr-3"></div> Formation Incluse
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl bg-[#6352ff] text-white text-center text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-title transition-all duration-300">Lancer ma boutique</a>
      </div>
      </div>

  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-16 reveal">
    <p class="text-title/50 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
      Besoin d'une offre sur-mesure ?<br class="block md:hidden" />
      <a href="#contact" class="text-[#d363ff] hover:underline underline-offset-4 ml-2">Parlons de votre projet</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="w-full h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-[#d363ff]/40 to-transparent"></div>